    "project_template_level_name": "CSA U7L4-L1 Private PBT_alt-2025",
    "teacher_markdown": "Students should conclude that the `getRecommendedMeatRecipes()` method should be `public` because it is meant to be called outside the `RecipeBlog` class.\r\n\r\nWhen students change the `recipesToString()` method to `private`, the functionality of the program is not impacted because it is only called inside the `RecipeBlog` class. With the design and structure of the program, there is no reason for another class to call this method.",
